00026 // Generic test for success on any status value (non-negative numbers
00027 // indicate success).
00028 //
00029 
00030 #define NT_SUCCESS(Status) ((NTSTATUS)(Status) >= 0)

00033 // Generic test for information on any status value.
00034 //
